snippet.title: Guardians of the Galaxy Movie Review - SPOILERS : Beyond The Trailer

localized.description:
Guardians of the Galaxy movie review with SPOILERS, end credits!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph shares her review today for this Marvel movie!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Guardians of the Galaxy Movie Review with spoilers!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph gives you her own review aka reaction to Guardians of the Galaxy in detail!  Does Marvel Studios have another hit?  Thoughts on Peter Quill aka Star-Lord, Gamora, Drax the Destroyer, Rocket Raccoon, Groot, Thanos, Ronan, Nebula, The Collector, Nova Corp and more!  Plus those End Credits! Should you see the full movie?  Enjoy this spoiler review of Guardians of the Galaxy in 2014, and make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for movie news, trailer and review on YouTube today!
